title: Skipping cancelled enqueue attempt with queue not closed
body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Bug description

training doesn't start with "Skipping cancelled enqueue attempt with queue not closed" error.

### Operating System

Ubuntu 18.0.4

### DeepLabCut version

2.2.0.1

### DeepLabCut mode

single animal

### Device type

NVIDIA Quadro RTX 8000

### Steps To Reproduce

I'm running on a high performance computing cluster. 
I am able to do initial training with the resnet50 as the initial weight, but when I try to retrain with the initial weight to the previously trained snapshot, I get the following error. But I'm not sure if it has to do with the initial weights or not.
